  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nYannick requested the best Manus skills for import. Manus identified and compiled over 100 skills from 7 verified GitHub repositories, creating a curated guide with categorized recommendations tailored to Yannick's role as Architect of New Society. The assistant clarified that it found real skill data but generated the comprehensive guide structure and personalized curation.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser seeking to enhance Manus capabilities by importing relevant skills from available repositories\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nSearched skill repositories using internet-skill-finder, analyzed available skills, categorized by function, and created personalized recommendations based on user profile\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [comprehensive_guide] Best Manus Skills Import Guide — Curated catalog of 100+ skills from 7 repositories with categories and personalized recommendations\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Prioritized skills relevant to societal transformation work\n- Organized skills by functional categories\n- Generated personalized curation rather than raw data dump\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Skill repository search function\n- Personalized curation approach\n- Clear categorization\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Multiple verified skill repositories available\n- Skills span diverse functional categories\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- Should real-time GitHub data be fetched for most current information?\n- Which specific skills should be prioritized for import?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Review recommended skills for import\n- Consider fetching real-time repository data\n- Implement priority skills into Manus system\n---\nUID: YwyPBBuKtnmXLz0MNq0ZQ1 | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0114\n"
}